{"tid":293897,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[x-post][封殺]中国廣電總局要求新浪微博,鳳凰網,AcFun停播網上視聽節目","createTime":"2017-06-22T14:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T14:00:42.000Z","uid":26506,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f009378759dfac189c78ee547fe2dae8710e09b8","tid":293897,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T14:00:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/china/%E6%89%B9%E5%AE%A3%E6%8F%9A%E8%B2%A0%E9%9D%A2%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96-%E5%BB%A3%E9%9B%BB%E7%B8%BD%E5%B1%80%E5%B0%81%E6%AE%BA%E6%96%B0%E6%B5%AA%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9A-%E9%B3%B3%E5%87%B0%E7%B6%B2%E8%A6%96%E8%81%BD%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%2589%25B9%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E6%258F%259A%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E9%259D%25A2%25E8%25A8%2580%25E8%25AB%2596-%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E9%259B%25BB%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%25B0%2581%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25B5%25AA%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E5%258D%259A-%25E9%25B3%25B3%25E5%2587%25B0%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E8%25A6%2596%25E8%2581%25BD%25E7%25AF%2580%25E7%259B%25AE%2F&d=2SecmFy%2BHa07roBAaDUWiAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=98635fc5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%2589%25B9%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E6%258F%259A%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E9%259D%25A2%25E8%25A8%2580%25E8%25AB%2596-%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E9%259B%25BB%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%25B0%2581%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25B5%25AA%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E5%258D%259A-%25E9%25B3%25B3%25E5%2587%25B0%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E8%25A6%2596%25E8%2581%25BD%25E7%25AF%2580%25E7%259B%25AE%2F&h=0c7e18a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/china/%E6%89%B9%E5%AE%A3%E6%8F%9A%E8%B2%A0%E9%9D%A2%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96-%E5%BB%A3%E9%9B%BB%E7%B8%BD%E5%B1%80%E5%B0%81%E6%AE%BA%E6%96%B0%E6%B5%AA%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9A-%E9%B3%B3%E5%87%B0%E7%B6%B2%E8%A6%96%E8%81%BD%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE/</a><br />\n批宣揚負面言論　廣電總局封殺新浪微博、鳳凰網視聽節目<br />\n2017/6/22 &mdash; 19:48<br />\n<br />\n中共再度出手整頓大陸媒體。國家新聞出版廣電總局發出通告，指新浪微博及鳳凰網等網站，在沒有許可證之下開展視聽節目服務，大量播放不符合規定的時政類視聽節目，及宣揚負面言論的節目，已責成相關部門停止視聽節目服務。消息令在美國上市的微博，在開市前急挫近7%。<br />\n<br />\n廣電總局的通告指，新浪微博、ACFUN、鳳凰網等網站在不具備《信息網絡傳播視聽節目許可證》的情況下開展視聽節目服務，並且大量播放不符合國家規定的時政類視聽節目和宣揚負面言論的社會評論性節目。<br />\n<br />\n廣電總局近日發函責成屬地管理部門，按照《互聯網視聽節目服務管理規定》，採取有效措施關停上述網站上的視聽節目服務，「進行全面整改，為廣大網民營造一個更加清朗的網絡空間」。<br />\n<br />\n中國當局早前亦以「營造健康向上主流輿論環境」為名，大力打擊娛樂新聞的社交媒體帳號，先獲關閉了多個八卦、狗仔帳戶，連「芭莎娛樂」、「南都娛樂週刊」等知名媒體的娛樂新聞帳戶，都成為被封殺的目標。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新浪微博鳳凰網停播被要求停播不合政策視聽節目<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1337695-20170622.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1337695-20170622.htm&d=2SecmFy%2BHa07roBAaDUWiAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=1256e0fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1337695-20170622.htm&h=3235ee70\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1337695-20170622.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n【冇片睇？】微博被指令停辦視聽節目服務 開市前大跌7%<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170622/56863772\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170622%2F56863772&d=2SecmFy%2BHa07roBAaDUWiAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=cfe118a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170622%2F56863772&h=35bc6205\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170622/56863772</a><br />\n<br />\n【乜都冇得睇】廣電局下令：微博鳳凰網等停播視聽節目 微博急挫6%<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170622/s00002/1498127882826\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170622%2Fs00002%2F1498127882826&d=2SecmFy%2BHa07roBAaDUWiAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=6abfbb8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170622%2Fs00002%2F1498127882826&h=4273cf16\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170622/s00002/1498127882826</a><br />\n[url][/url]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n批宣揚負面言論　廣電總局封殺新浪微博、鳳凰網視聽節目<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/293836/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/293836/page/1</a>"}]}